### Testes das Novas Rotas de Usuário
### Arquivo HTTP para testar os endpoints criados no IdentityController

@baseUrl = https://localhost:7139
@apiVersion = 1.0
@token = seu-token-jwt-aqui

### 1. Fazer Login (obter token JWT)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v{{apiVersion}}/identity/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@exemplo.com",
  "password": "Admin@123"
}

### 2. Listar Usuários (Paginação - Página 1, 10 itens)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v{{apiVersion}}/identity?pageNumber=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 3. Listar Usuários (Paginação - Página 2, 5 itens)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v{{apiVersion}}/identity?pageNumber=2&pageSize=5
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4. Buscar Usuário por ID (existente)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v{{apiVersion}}/identity/3fa85f64-5717-4562-b3fc-2c963f66afa6
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 5. Atualizar Usuário
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v{{apiVersion}}/identity/3fa85f64-5717-4562-b3fc-2c963f66afa6
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "3fa85f64-5717-4562-b3fc-2c963f66afa6"
}

### 6. Atualizar Usuário (erro: ID incompatível)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v{{apiVersion}}/identity/3fa85f64-5717-4562-b3fc-2c963f66afa6
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000"
}

### 7. Deletar Usuário
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v{{apiVersion}}/identity/3fa85f64-5717-4562-b3fc-2c963f66afa6
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 8. Tentar buscar usuário deletado (deve retornar 404)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v{{apiVersion}}/identity/3fa85f64-5717-4562-b3fc-2c963f66afa6
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 9. Registrar novo usuário
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v{{apiVersion}}/identity/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "novousuario@exemplo.com",
  "password": "SenhaSegura@123",
  "firstName": "Novo",
  "lastName": "Usuário"
}

### 10. Listar todos os usuários novamente
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v{{apiVersion}}/identity?pageNumber=1&pageSize=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

